    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This is not possible with the numeric refinements method indeed, but it is possible with raw filters:\r\n\r\n```\r\nhelper.addQueryParameter('filters', 'rooms=42 OR rooms=56 OR rooms>=37')\r\n```",
