  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "@Haroenv Thanks for you reply\r\n\r\nThis approach won't work if you have any other regular numeric filter:\r\n\r\nIf you use `helper.addQueryParameter` and then use any regular numeric filter you'll get the following error:\r\n\r\n `[Numeric filters] Can't switch from the advanced to the managed API. It is probably an error, if this is really what you want, you have to first clear the numeric filters.`\r\n\r\n and viceversa:\r\n\r\n `[Numeric filters] Can't switch from the managed API to the advanced. It is probably an error, if this is really what you want, you have to first clear the numeric filters.`\r\n\r\nIs there anything someone can use to get it to work ?",
    "created_at": "2019-10-03T19:14:37Z",
